This is very simple dashboard for tracking outstanding bugs in Ironic.

It is a Flask application and can be run as such. For local testing use:

   $ tox -erun

It is also set to run on openshift and actually runs on
http://dashboard-ironic.7e14.starter-us-west-2.openshiftapps.com/

